<section>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="small-6 small-centered columns">
				<h3>Where?</h3>
				<p>The ceremony and reception will be taking place at <a href="http://hawthornestates.ca">Hawthorn&nbsp;Estates</a>.
				<ul>
					<li>From Winnipeg, take Highway 59 North.</li>
					<li>Exit right on Highway 44 East.</li>
					<li>Drive 11 km on Highway 44.</li>
